{"tid":1972990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：新加坡貿易部長罵得好。香港人不只是低能和丟臉，而是愚昧、賤格、卑劣。","createTime":"2020-04-15T01:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T07:15:13.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cfb6d998079a0f9353a71c23495d3391d65544fc","tid":1972990,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T01:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UECKTS9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUECKTS9.png&h=f81fd3f2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n新加坡規定民眾出外強制戴口罩 只能在運動時脫下<br />\n2020-04-14 19:55 聯合報 <br />\n新加坡國家發展部部長黃循財14日宣布，為了防止新冠肺炎傳播，即起民眾出門強制戴口罩，只有兩歲以下幼童不必戴，新規定即刻生效，初犯者不予勸導，立刻罰300新幣（約台幣6400元）。<br />\n外出民眾只能在運動時拿下口罩，如慢跑或跑步時，但運動完畢後須立刻戴上。<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/120944/4491766\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F120944%2F4491766&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=cba5f00c\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/120944/4491766</a>"},{"pid":"50782b16ebf25fc386e20fb24ea3d466e8dc628c","tid":1972990,"uid":74622,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T01:36:42.000Z","msg":"我諗冇人想知佢講乜"},{"pid":"a5466657bfa0841f4ec72a1a1b367f7e3ba5ec72","tid":1972990,"uid":61348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T01:39:46.000Z","msg":"淨係認同香港人係低能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a37abdec772e0e39384d4ff3f9e972a5765e91","tid":1972990,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T01:40:36.000Z","msg":"邵家臻議員為還押手足發起「和你做筆友」計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1972952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1972952</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e7bca293887b41ec1cac51ab66df1687cccc2439","tid":1972990,"uid":22087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T01:40:37.000Z","msg":"binc"},{"pid":"7ce66d2fd9cfd203cec2c20437fde255afd2bd11","